snippet.title: Kura5 Bonds of the Undying - Chapter 3 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Kura5's third chapter (version 0.4) is now out on itchio 

(Trailer made by FlashTrickstar!)

New This Update
-New story chapter (1 immortal dungeon + 2 undead dungeons)
-New items/weapons/summons
-New San Miguel Citizens (Bianca, Russell, Holliday)
-New Music tracks (Boktai remix tracks are free, you can get the official ost on Lapin's bandcamp)
-Updated La Lupe and Von Linnell's portriats
-Additional Locke and Mac's sidequests
-Multiple Save Slots
-Gameplay tweaks to combat, status effects, and stealth
-Various Bug fixes from the previous release

Music by LiteralLapin
